sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG delivers heritage style with premium materials and responsive cushioning.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Lucky Green
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG delivers heritage style with premium materials and responsive cushioning.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shattered Backboard'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Shattered Backboard features a color scheme inspired by Michael Jordan's famous dunk that shattered the backboard during a Nike exhibition game in 1985. It combines black, white, and orange tones for a bold and unique look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'White Cement'
sneakers.description: Retro inspires retro with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'White Cement,' featuring the iconic elephant print from by the Air Jordan 3. The high-top sneaker displays a sleek grey leather overlay against a pristine white leather base with black leather accents on the collar and Swoosh. The tongue is marked with a woven Nike Air tag, and the lateral collar is stamped with the iconic Wings logo. Cushioned comfort is guaranteed with Air-sole technology in the midsole while the aged off-white midsole sits on a durable grey rubber outsole.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'University Blue'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 University Blue features a combination of white and University Blue leather on the upper with black accents. It offers a clean and stylish look with a pop of color.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Dark Mochas'
sneakers.description: The Dark Mochas sneakers feature a sleek combination of dark brown, black, and sail tones. These Air Jordan 1s offer a sophisticated and stylish look with premium materials and a classic design.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Yellow Toe'
sneakers.description: The Yellow Toe sneakers make a bold statement with their vibrant color scheme. These Air Jordan 1s feature a striking combination of black, white, and vibrant yellow, adding a pop of color to your outfit.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Skyline'
sneakers.description: The Skyline sneakers bring a fresh and modern twist to the Air Jordan 1 silhouette. With a mix of various shades of blue and gray, these sneakers offer a contemporary and urban aesthetic.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Black White'
sneakers.description: The Black/White Air Jordan 1s are a classic colorway that never goes out of style. With a timeless combination of black and white, these sneakers offer a clean and versatile look suitable for any occasion.

sneakers.name: Travis Scott x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Mocha'
sneakers.description: The Travis Scott x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Mocha' collaboration is a highly sought-after release. These sneakers feature a unique blend of brown, black, and white, with Travis Scott's signature branding and design elements.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'UNC Toe'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'UNC Toe' pays homage to Michael Jordan's alma mater, the University of North Carolina. Featuring a combination of white, university blue, and black, these sneakers offer a classic and clean look with a touch of UNC-inspired style.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Stage Haze'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Stage Haze' features a unique and eye-catching colorway with a combination of purple, pink, and black. These sneakers offer a vibrant and energetic look with premium materials and classic Air Jordan 1 design.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Washed Black'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Washed Black' showcases a worn-in, distressed aesthetic with its washed black leather upper. These sneakers offer a vintage and rugged look with a touch of timeless style.

sneakers.name: Off-White x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'UNC'
sneakers.description: The Off-White x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'UNC' is a highly coveted collaboration between Off-White and Jordan Brand. Featuring Virgil Abloh's signature deconstructed design elements, these sneakers combine a classic UNC-inspired color scheme with unique Off-White branding.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Royal Toe'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Royal Toe' features a timeless colorway that combines black, white, and royal blue. These sneakers offer a classic and versatile look with premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 silhouette.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 High 'Chicago' 1985
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 High 'Chicago' 1985 pays homage to the original 1985 release of the Air Jordan 1. With its iconic red, white, and black color scheme, these sneakers offer a nostalgic and classic look with a touch of basketball history.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Obsidian'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Obsidian' showcases a rich combination of navy blue, white, and university blue. These sneakers offer a clean and sophisticated look with premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 design.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Hyper Royal'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Hyper Royal' features a refreshing color combination of hyper royal, sail, and white. These sneakers offer a vibrant and stylish look with premium materials and classic Air Jordan 1 design.

sneakers.name: WMNS Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Reverse Laney'
sneakers.description: The WMNS Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Reverse Laney' offers a unique twist to the Laney High School color scheme. These sneakers feature a vibrant combination of varsity maize, game royal, and white, offering a bold and stylish look for women.

sneakers.name: WMNS Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Stealth'
sneakers.description: The WMNS Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Stealth' offers a versatile and stylish option for women. These sneakers feature a combination of black, white, and stealth gray, providing a sleek and modern look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Dark Marina Blue'
sneakers.description: TThe Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Dark Marina Blue’ dresses the iconic silhouette in classic two-tone color blocking. The all-leather upper features a black base with contrasting dark blue overlays along the forefoot, heel, collar and eyestay. A matching blue Swoosh is accompanied by a Jordan Wings logo stamped in black on the lateral collar flap. Atop the nylon tongue, a woven Nike Air tag nods to the shoe’s retro cushioning technology: an Air-sole unit encapsulated in polyurethane nestled in the heel of the rubber cupsole.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Court Purple 2.0'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Court Purple 2.0' offers a fresh take on the classic color blocking. These sneakers feature a combination of court purple, white, and black, providing a clean and vibrant look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Alternate Bred'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Alternate Bred' offers a stylish and versatile option for everyday wear. These sneakers feature a combination of black, gym red, and white, providing a classic and timeless look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Perforated - White University Gold'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Perforated - White University Gold' combines classic design with modern details. These sneakers feature a combination of white, university gold, and black, offering a clean and sophisticated look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shattered Backboard 3.0'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shattered Backboard 3.0' is the third iteration of the popular Shattered Backboard series. These sneakers feature a unique color scheme inspired by the orange and black uniform Michael Jordan wore during an exhibition game in Italy, offering a bold and iconic look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Gorge Green'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Gorge Green' showcases a striking color combination of gorge green, white, and black. These sneakers offer a bold and eye-catching look with premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 silhouette.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shadow 2.0'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shadow 2.0' puts a new twist on the classic Shadow colorway. These sneakers feature a combination of black, light smoke gray, and white, offering a sleek and versatile look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Pine Green 2.0'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Pine Green 2.0' offers a fresh take on the classic Pine Green colorway. These sneakers feature a combination of pine green, white, and black, providing a clean and vibrant look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Brotherhood'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Brotherhood' pays tribute to the camaraderie and unity among basketball players. These sneakers feature a combination of royal blue, white, and black, offering a classic and timeless look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High '85 'Georgetown'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High '85 'Georgetown' pays homage to the Georgetown University basketball team. These sneakers feature a combination of navy blue, gray, and white, offering a classic and collegiate-inspired look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Stealth'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Stealth' offers a sleek and stylish look with its combination of black, white, and stealth gray. These sneakers feature premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 design.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Patent Bred'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Patent Bred' features a bold and vibrant colorway with its patent leather construction. These sneakers offer a sleek and glossy look, combining black and red tones.

sneakers.name: WMNS Air Jordan 1 High OG 'UNC to Chicago'
sneakers.description: The WMNS Air Jordan 1 High OG 'UNC to Chicago' showcases a unique color transition from University Blue to Gym Red. These sneakers offer a striking and eye-catching look with premium materials and a combination of iconic colorways.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 High Golf 'Panda'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 High Golf 'Panda' is a unique golf shoe that takes inspiration from the classic Air Jordan 1 silhouette. These sneakers feature a black and white color scheme with a spikeless outsole, offering both style and functionality on the golf course.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Utility 'Quai 54' 2022
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Utility 'Quai 54' 2022 is a special edition sneaker released in conjunction with the annual Quai 54 street basketball tournament. These sneakers feature a unique design with vibrant colors, paying tribute to the tournament's vibrant and diverse culture.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shadow' 2018
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Shadow' 2018 is a reissue of the popular Shadow colorway from 1985. These sneakers feature a combination of black and medium gray, offering a versatile and classic look with a touch of nostalgia.

sneakers.name: WMNS Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Silver Toe'
sneakers.description: The WMNS Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Silver Toe' showcases a sleek and stylish design with its silver and black color scheme. These sneakers offer a luxurious and eye-catching look with premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 silhouette.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Bordeaux'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Bordeaux' offers a sophisticated and luxurious look with its combination of burgundy, black, and white. These sneakers feature premium materials and a classic design, making them a versatile and stylish choice.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Game Royal'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Game Royal' offers a bold and vibrant look with its combination of game royal, black, and white. These sneakers feature premium materials and the iconic Air Jordan 1 design, making them a must-have for any sneaker enthusiast.

sneakers.name: Nigel Sylvester x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Nigel Sylvester'
sneakers.description: The Nigel Sylvester x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Nigel Sylvester' is a special collaboration with BMX rider Nigel Sylvester. These sneakers feature a unique design inspired by Nigel's personal style and BMX culture, offering a distinctive and urban look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High SB 'LA to Chicago'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High SB 'LA to Chicago' is a special edition sneaker that pays homage to the journey from Los Angeles to Chicago. These sneakers feature a color-changing design that reveals Chicago-inspired colors when worn or aged, offering a unique and dynamic look.

sneakers.name: Fragment Design x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG
sneakers.description: The Fragment Design x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG is a highly sought-after collaboration with renowned designer Hiroshi Fujiwara. These sneakers feature a clean and minimalistic design with Fragment Design branding, offering a sophisticated and stylish look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Turbo Green'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Turbo Green' offers a unique and vintage-inspired look with its combination of turbo green, white, and light smoke gray. These sneakers feature a distressed and worn-in aesthetic, offering a stylish and fashionable choice.

sneakers.name: Off-White x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'White' 2018
sneakers.description: The Off-White x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'White' 2018 is a highly sought-after collaboration between Off-White and Jordan Brand. These sneakers feature Virgil Abloh's signature deconstructed design with unique detailing and text throughout, offering a distinct and fashionable look.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Heirloom'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Heirloom' offers a premium and luxurious look with its combination of black, metallic gold, and white. These sneakers feature premium materials and a sleek design, making them a sophisticated and stylish choice.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort 'Chile Red'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort 'Chile Red' offers a modern and comfortable twist to the classic Air Jordan 1 silhouette. These sneakers feature Zoom Air cushioning and a vibrant chile red colorway, offering both style and enhanced comfort.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Patina'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Patina' features a unique patina finish on its leather upper, offering a vintage and worn-in look. These sneakers showcase a combination of bronze, black, and sail colors, providing a stylish and distinct appearance.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PRM 'Yin Yang'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PRM 'Yin Yang' offers a clean and minimalistic design with its black and white color scheme. These sneakers feature premium materials and a timeless look, making them a versatile and stylish choice.

sneakers.name: Lance Mountain x Air Jordan 1 Retro SB QS 'Black'
sneakers.description: The Lance Mountain x Air Jordan 1 Retro SB QS 'Black' is a special collaboration with professional skateboarder Lance Mountain. These sneakers feature a unique design with black and white paint splatters, offering a rugged and artistic look inspired by the skateboarding culture.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 2 Retro
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 2 Retro features a sleek design and luxurious materials for a premium look and feel.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 3 Retro features a sleek design and luxurious materials for a premium look and feel.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Bred'
sneakers.description: Banned by the NBA in 1985, Michael Jordan was charged $5,000 per game for wearing the Air Jordan 1 ‘Black/Red' because they didn’t include the color white which was part of the Chicago Bulls’ official team colors. Used as a marketing tactic, Nike crafted the ‘Banned’ campaign around the sneakers to launch and promote the Air Jordan line. The sneaker was retroed in 1994, 2011, 2013 and 2016. The 2011 pair features an ‘X’ on the heel paying homage to the 'Banned' nickname.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro KO High 'Sport Blue'
sneakers.description: The Jordan Brand brought back the Air Jordan 1 KO High in a Sport Blue colorway in August 2014. A canvas successor to the original 1985 silhouette, the high-top swaps out the traditional AJ1 tooling for a midsole reminiscent of the Nike Vandal. The distinctive black and blue color blocking, similar to the iconic ‘Royal’ colorway of the Air Jordan 1, is featured on a full canvas build, complemented with a leather Swoosh and Nike branding on the lightly padded nylon tongue.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro OG High 'Jeter'
sneakers.description: The ‘Jeter’ colorway celebrated Derek Jeter’s retirement from baseball with a Yankees-inspired theme. Other features include metallic gold Jeter logos on the tongues, Wings logos on the ankles, and Jumpman logos on the heels. Released in September 2014, the shoe was released at Foot Action's Flight 23 in NYC alongside a similar colorway of the Flight Flex Trainer.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro OG High 'Washed Black'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Washed Black' is an updated version of the classic silhouette and features a neutral color palette. The leather upper appears in white with grey suede overlays and a matching Swoosh logo. The high-cut collar appears in a lighter shade of grey suede and has an ankle flap with the trademark Wings logo. The breathable nylon tongue features a woven black and red Nike tag which provides a subtle pop of color. The shoe is supported by a traditional off-white midsole atop a black rubber outsole for excellent grip.

sneakers.name: MARVEL X AIR JORDAN 1 RETRO HIGH OG 'NEXT CHAPTER'
sneakers.description: The Marvel x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Next Chapter' is a collaboration whose colorway is inspired by the animated film 'Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse.’ This version of the iconic sneaker model is a creative twist on the classic ‘Chicago’ colorway, with a white leather upper and black patent leather on the signature Swoosh and collar. The scarlet overlays are a combination of various textures and prints, pieced together to create a unique design that references the complex nature of the Spiderman universe. The shoe is supported by a rubber cupsole that combines aged sidewalls with a crimson semi-clear rubber outsole. A Nike tag made of woven nylon decorates the tongue while the retro Wings logo is stamped on the lateral collar flap.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro OG High 'Palomino'
sneakers.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Palomino' combines a lavish design with classic color blocking inspired by the original version. The legendary shoe boasts a black leather upper with weathered brown nubuck accents on the toe box, heel overlay, collar flap and Swoosh. The lateral side of the collar flap features a black Wings logo, while a Nike logo in metallic gold lettering adorns the woven tongue tag. The midsole is finished in an off-white shade and features enclosed Air-sole cushioning and stitched sidewall construction. The brown rubber outsole has a grip pattern that provides optimal traction on the court.

sneakers.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro OG High 'Electro Orange'
Air Jordan 1 Retro OG High 'Stealth'
sneakers.description: The iconic original is delivered in a refined color palette with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Stealth.’ The toe box with airy perforations, heel and collar overlays and signature Swoosh all appear in light grey leather against a base of white. Nike Air branding appears on the ventilated nylon tongue tag and the collar is adorned with a classic Wings logo. A traditional rubber cupsole forms the foundation of the shoe and features an interior Air-sole unit in the heel for cushioned comfort.
